  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/cb57630c166024cbf2a7c64336e8360d.poster.avif?t=1725900139\" width=92 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/cb57630c166024cbf2a7c64336e8360d.webm?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/cb57630c166024cbf2a7c64336e8360d.mp4?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>An abandoned chapel. <br>An old generator that won't start. <br>Someone or something else. <br>And not just one of them.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/7338bfea500c1aa05be964af5a784db1.poster.avif?t=1725900139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/7338bfea500c1aa05be964af5a784db1.webm?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/7338bfea500c1aa05be964af5a784db1.mp4?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The hours here feel like weeks, but you have to endure it. You must find out the truth. About what? Even you don't really remember that well.<br>\"revere\" is a found footage survival horror game that takes the point and click mechanics of Five Nights at Freddy's and combines them with puzzles and minigames.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/b1e131b389238bc4eba4cb23f8000a67.poster.avif?t=1725900139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/b1e131b389238bc4eba4cb23f8000a67.webm?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/b1e131b389238bc4eba4cb23f8000a67.mp4?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> With each stage you have a different objective and a new added foe to fight. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/c1e8e46e3d725848d51b80773b80d257.poster.avif?t=1725900139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/c1e8e46e3d725848d51b80773b80d257.webm?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/c1e8e46e3d725848d51b80773b80d257.mp4?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The one thing that stays the same is that you still have to keep 'them' away. At all costs. The question is, do you have what it takes?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/cb57630c166024cbf2a7c64336e8360d.poster.avif?t=1725900139\" width=92 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/cb57630c166024cbf2a7c64336e8360d.webm?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1956330/extras/cb57630c166024cbf2a7c64336e8360d.mp4?t=1725900139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
